          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Competitor content breakdown with term frequency</h4><p>See exactly which terms each competitor uses and how often. More actionable than a simple term list.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>AI content generation with NLP targeting built in</h4><p>Generate content that's already optimized for your target terms. No separate optimization step required.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: less intuitive interface than Clearscope or Surfer</h4><p>NeuronWriter has a steeper learning curve. Plan for 1-2 hours to get comfortable with the workflow before you hit full productivity.</p></div></li>
