        <p style="color: var(--text-3); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px;"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Bronze $23/mo (15 analyses, 15,000 AI words) · Silver $37/mo (45 analyses, 30,000 AI words) · Gold $57/mo (90 analyses, 60,000 AI words)</p>
