      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#6 · $49-99/MO · BEST WITH REAL-TIME SERP DATA</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">SEO.AI — Best for real-time SERP-informed writing</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For writers who want live SERP data updating their optimization recommendations as they type.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">SEO.AI combines content optimization with live SERP analysis. While you write or generate content, the tool pulls real-time data from Google's results — not cached snapshots. If a competitor publishes a new article this morning, SEO.AI's recommendations reflect it. The keyword clustering feature also helps build topical authority across related keyword groups.</p>
