        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Outranking approaches content optimization from the strategy layer. Instead of starting with a blank editor, it starts with your entire site's Google Search Console data. It identifies content gaps against competitors, surfaces pages losing rankings, and generates AI briefs for both new content and refreshes. Direct WordPress publishing makes the execution side clean.</p>
