        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">GrowthBar combines content optimization scoring with AI writing in a straightforward interface. It's not as accurate as Surfer, but the learning curve is minimal and the all-in-one approach fits solo operators who don't want to manage a stack of separate tools. The Chrome extension adds SERP data directly to Google search results without opening a dashboard.</p>
